          Get Early Access
        </a>
        <a href="/animal-records" class="inline-block bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white hover:text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] transition text-center" style="min-height: 44px;">
          See animal records →
